  physical_appearance: This is a black-and-white photograph. It features a section of a tower of silence
 with several tall trees peeking above the structure
 and birds flying in and amongst the tree canopies. The rounded edge of the tower can be seen on the bottom of the photograph
 with a doorway in the foreground. There is an inscription in the top-right of the photoraph. The photograph is slightly stained on the top-left corner.
